<div class="about-cameron fade-up">
  <div class="about-cameron__text">
    <h2 class="about-cameron__heading">RUPP CONSTRUCTION & CONCRETE LLC</h2>

    <p>
      Cameron Rupp founded Rupp Construction & Concrete in 2021 with a simple goal: do concrete
      work the way he'd want it done at his own house. That means showing up when he says he will,
      bidding honest numbers, and not leaving until the job is right.
    </p>
    <p>
      Based in Enumclaw, Cameron and his crew serve residential and commercial customers across
      Auburn, Federal Way, Renton, Kent, Maple Valley, Bonney Lake, Covington, Sumner, Buckley,
      and the surrounding Puget Sound area. Most projects are quoted within 24 hours and started
      within the week.
    </p>
    <p>
      With over 52 five-star Google reviews and a $1M insurance policy, Rupp Construction is a
      company you can trust with your property. Cameron personally oversees every job from the
      first site visit through the final walkthrough.
    </p>

    <dl class="about-cameron__credentials">
      <div class="about-cameron__cred-row">
        <dt>WA LICENSE</dt>
        <dd>RUPPCCC799L2</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="about-cameron__cred-row">
        <dt>INSURANCE</dt>
        <dd>$1,000,000 — Western World Ins Co</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="about-cameron__cred-row">
        <dt>ESTABLISHED</dt>
        <dd>2021</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="about-cameron__cred-row">
        <dt>GOOGLE RATING</dt>
        <dd>★★★★★ 52 Reviews</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>

  <div class="about-cameron__photos">
    <img
      src="/images/rupp-construction-team04.jpg"
      alt="Cameron Rupp smiling in hi-vis green hoodie at a concrete job site"
      loading="lazy"
      class="about-cameron__photo"
    />
    <img
      src="/images/rupp-construction-team01.jpg"
      alt="Cameron Rupp with supplier in front of concrete truck at golden hour"
      loading="lazy"
      class="about-cameron__photo"
    />
    <img
      src="/images/rupp-construction-team02.jpg"
      alt="Rupp Construction branded work truck with bulldog logo"
      loading="lazy"
      class="about-cameron__photo"
    />
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .about-cameron {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .about-cameron__heading {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-cameron__text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-cameron__credentials {
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .about-cameron__cred-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .about-cameron__cred-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .about-cameron__cred-row dt {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .about-cameron__cred-row dd {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin: 0;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .about-cameron__photos {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-cameron__photo {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-cameron {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: start;
    }
  }
</style>
